    "advancement": [],
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"439\" data-end=\"481\">Shared Burden (Reaction; PB/Long Rest)</strong><br data-start=\"481\" data-end=\"484\" />You willingly take the pain of others upon yourself.</p><p data-start=\"538\" data-end=\"692\">When an ally within <strong data-start=\"558\" data-end=\"569\">10 feet</strong> of you takes damage, you may use your <strong data-start=\"608\" data-end=\"620\">reaction</strong> to reduce that damage by an amount equal to your <strong data-start=\"670\" data-end=\"691\">proficiency bonus</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"694\" data-end=\"808\">You take <strong data-start=\"703\" data-end=\"749\">psychic damage equal to the amount reduced</strong>.<br data-start=\"750\" data-end=\"753\" />This psychic damage <strong data-start=\"773\" data-end=\"807\">cannot be reduced or prevented</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"810\" data-end=\"965\"><strong data-start=\"810\" data-end=\"819\">Uses:</strong> You can use this feature a number of times equal to your <strong data-start=\"877\" data-end=\"898\">proficiency bonus</strong>, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a <strong data-start=\"951\" data-end=\"964\">long rest</strong>.</p><p></p><p>[GAROU_FEATURE] id=shared-burden</p>",
